{"tid":1599353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"101 港島 定 五區","createTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T03:53:37.000Z","uid":61886,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b91c4671ec9471235d2942ed590bfa79d34b10b","tid":1599353,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:33:27.000Z","msg":"襯有時間大家拎個共識先<br />\n<br />\n港島 正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 務求用最多人數塞爆港島<br />\n- 有較多政府地標，例如政總、中聯辦<br />\n- 封鐵好難走，地形比狗玩到熟<br />\n- 考慮黨鐵提早封站，狗仔開波，和理非唔會出得晒出黎，情況似美領果次，唔會比你集到人，唔會再出現100萬人以上情況<br />\n<br />\n五區 負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 遍地開花，狗仔唔夠人守咁多地方<br />\n- 地區作戰，前線較易撤退，行路都返到屋企<br />\n- 街坊幫手加乘<br />\n- 唔夠記者處理多區戰線<br />\n- 顯示唔到上街既人數之多<br />\n<br />\n投票吧<br />\n希望大家有共識<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n我預計就算揀港島一區<br />\n封鐵封路加roadblock<br />\n未集到30萬人已開波<br />\n未出和理非亦會選擇轉場<br />\n最後轉為地區戰"},{"pid":"70953eba763b928e9bdab0abd6b8b6e15d86e580","tid":1599353,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"9cf1f249f5575fdeb5ddce320cfff2a2975229a1","tid":1599353,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"plan a plan b 咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n無封路無封鐵就港島<br />\n有封就即刻五區"},{"pid":"49ceda7529ff372518f6efefea605275eb765fe8","tid":1599353,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf1f249f5575fdeb5ddce320cfff2a2975229a1","tid":1599353,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"plan a plan b 咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n無封路無封鐵就港島<br />\n有封就即刻五區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"兩區/三區唔得咩 五區總有某d區既人太少就好危險"},{"pid":"2365697cdb7051e2dd8ce7dd1ba4e926a50c6799","tid":1599353,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:48:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac20ed7409f75db20f5999c9db219a0026e88400","tid":1599353,"uid":200069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"試下維港?<br />\n<br />\n十一 維港睇煙花？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51cc3fa66b7bf35b4898c17c7792e4f1b2e66a3a","tid":1599353,"uid":154258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:09:44.000Z","msg":"五區分散狗仔警力？<br />\n分散埋自己嘅力量呀屌"},{"pid":"23ff9c6f7ba6a25b2056d7459238fc796c0f9d2d","tid":1599353,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf1f249f5575fdeb5ddce320cfff2a2975229a1","tid":1599353,"uid":37722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:34:55.000Z","msg":"plan a plan b 咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n無封路無封鐵就港島<br />\n有封就即刻五區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:13:16.000Z","msg":"咁同配合政府部署有咩分別<br />\n主導權喺政府手"},{"pid":"c61d890f5685346d7091c994d8ef6ff6d7b117fc","tid":1599353,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"